{
  "texts": [
    "Researchers 113, 114 proposed an improved performance of predicting RUL based on a combination of denoising auto-encoder and Transformer network compared to regular MLP, RNN and LSTM.",
    "Furthermore, Cai et al.",
    "115 also proposed the efficacy of the transformer network based on fewer capacity data input.",
    "These studies show that ML can provide accurate predictions of the calendar lifetime of batteries, which can help accelerate the development of advanced batteries with longer calendar lifetimes.",
    "However, most reported studies focus on commercialized batteries, which limits the ability to provide insights into the development of new battery materials."
  ]
}